A CORDWALLES Preparatory School teacher, Mdu Mtshali (32) was found dead in the school’s swimming pool last Saturday. At approximately 1pm, ER24 paramedics arrived where they found another service provider on scene. It is believed the teacher was found by his family after he was reported missing. He was declared dead at the scene. The exact circumstances surrounding the incident is not yet known. — Supplied. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  